rubric.description: Students create an app to show a set of video or image steps to make different baking items. They also create a rubric to show an ingredient listing. ## Overview In this project, you will create an app to view video recipes. You will handle media loading, verify your user interfaces with UI tests, and integrate third party libraries. You'll also provide a complete user experience with a home screen widget. ## Project Rubric Your project will be evaluated by a Udacity Code Reviewer according to this rubric. Be sure to review it thoroughly before you submit. All criteria must "meet specifications" in order to pass.
